summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Parks and Recreation authorizing the purchase for park and recreation purposes (Fauntleroy Park) of certain property in Fenton's 1st Addition, Forest View Tracts, Forest Hills Division No. 2, unrecorded, Graham's Acre Tracts, unrecorded, Centry Scenic Acre Tracts, Daugherty Addition to the City of Seattle, and certain unplatted areas in Section 25, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M., King County, Washington; and making a partially reimbursable appropriation from the Park Acquisition and Development Fund therefor.
